entry.def: If you say that someone is bouncing with health, you mean that they are very healthy. You can also refer to a bouncing baby.

example.ex: They are bouncing with health in the good weather...
example.tran: 在这种宜人的天气里，他们健康活泼地茁壮成长。

example.ex: Derek is now the proud father of a bouncing baby girl.
example.tran: 德里克现在是一位自豪的父亲，他有一个健康的小女儿。
